high_descs: Walk towards the table at the end of the room.
Pick up the cup off of the table.
Turn to the left and face the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, set the cup in it, close the refrigerator, wait a second, open the refrigerator again, and remove the cup.
Turn to the left and face the sink.
Place the cup in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place the cup from the table in the sink.

grab a from from the table

place the cup inside of the fridge, and then take it back out
turn and walk towards the kitchen sink
place the cup in the sink

high_descs: Go towards the door.  Turn left at the table.  Turn and face the table.
Pick up the glass that is on the table.
Turn right and move forward.  Then turn right and face the sink.  Move forward and turn right and face the in front of the fridge.
Open the fridge. Set the glass on the top right shelf.  Shut the fridge.  Open the fridge.  Get the glass on the top right shelf.  Close the fridge.
Turn all the way around.  Go to the left and go to the sink.
Put the glass in to the sink.
anns.task_desc: Take a glass from the table, to the fridge, to the sink.
